---
title: Baked Beef & Feta Wraps with a Cucumber Salad
description: Chef Jesse has seasoned the beef mince filling in this recipe with paprika, cumin, adding red peppers, carrots and creamy feta for added layers of texture. Baked until crispy - we recommend serving everything up in the middle of your table and getting everyone to tuck in. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spicy-beef-wrap-598de63c-8f0fb39f.jpg
